aind_data_schema.core.subject.Housing
Description of subject housing
Attributes: cohoused_subjects (List[str]): List of IDs of other subjects housed in same cage. Default is [].

aind_data_schema.core.subject.LightCycle
Description of vivarium light cycle times
Attributes: lights_on_time (time): Time in UTC that lights were turned on lights_off_time (time): Time in UTC that lights were turned off

aind_data_schema.core.subject.Subject
Description of a subject of data collection
Attributes: subject_id (str): Unique identifier for the subject. If this is not a Allen LAS ID, indicate this in the Notes. genotype (Optional[str]): Genotype of the animal providing both alleles. Default is None. alleles (List[PIDName]): Allele names and persistent IDs. Default is []. source (Union[AllenInstitute, ColumbiaUniversity, HuazhongUniversityOfScienceAndTechnology, JacksonLaboratory, NewYorkUniversity, Other]): Where the subject was acquired from. If bred in-house, use Allen Institute. rrid (Optional[PIDName]): RRID of mouse if acquired from supplier. Default is None. restrictions (Optional[str]): Any restrictions on use or publishing based on subject source. Default is None.
